OL,3,CThree pensioners among four arrested
OL,4,Cby police investigating modern slavery
OL,6,FFour men - three of them pensioners -
OL,7,Fhave been arrested as part of an
OL,8,Finvestigation into modern slavery.
OL,10,FRaids took place at seven addresses in
OL,11,FLiverpool and Sefton, in Merseyside,
OL,12,Fon 29 May, by officers acting
OL,13,Ffollowing intelligence of men
OL,14,Fallegedly targeting vulnerable people.
OL,16,FThe men, aged between 63 and 77, were
OL,17,Ftaken into custody and are also being
OL,18,Fquestioned about alleged drug
OL,19,Foffences, Merseyside Police said.
