OL,3,CThree pensioners among four arrested
OL,4,Cby police investigating modern slavery
OL,6,FOfficers also seized cash, a lock
OL,7,Fknife and mobile phones.
OL,9,FThose arrested are:
OL,11,FA reception centre for victims has
OL,12,Fbeen established where they are
OL,13,Freceiving the support of officers and
OL,14,Frelevant support agencies.
