OL,3,CThree pensioners among four arrested
OL,4,Cby police investigating modern slavery
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Siobhan
OL,7,FRussell said: "We take all reports
OL,8,Fextremely seriously and encourage any
OL,9,Fvictim to come forward. We have
OL,10,Fspecialist officers who will treat
OL,11,Fyour reports sensitively and support
OL,12,Fyou throughout the whole legal process.
OL,14,F"We simply will not tolerate criminals
OL,15,Fwho bring misery and harm to other
OL,16,Fpeople. They ruin lives and care only
OL,17,Fabout lining their own pockets by
OL,18,Fexploiting others.
OL,26,@oD@OOUvD@AOU
