OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780081925
OL,3,CThree pensioners among four arrested
OL,4,Cby police investigating modern slavery
OL,6,F"Information from the public is vital
OL,7,Fin building a clearer picture of the
OL,8,Fnetworks involved in modern slavery
OL,9,Fand ensuring perpetrators are brought
OL,10,Fto justice, so that we can protect
OL,11,Fvictims from further harm."
OL,13,FAnyone with information on vulnerable
OL,14,Fpeople being exploited should contact
OL,15,FMerseyside Police social media desk
OL,16,Fvia X or Facebook @MerPolCC
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]
